devdoc.details: Contract module for Tranfering the Contract ownership. This module is used to transfer the Ownership of the Contract to a new Owner who is not BlackListed but is an Admin.

params._owner: address The address which owns the funds.
params._spender: address The address which will spend the funds.

returns.remaining: A uint specifying the amount of tokens still available for the spender.
